t is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.', 'Есть вопросы?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contact-form-1', '', '', '2020-07-01 12:40:43', '2020-07-01 09:40:43', '', 0, 'http://flowers.local/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=65', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
